workouts.introText:
Challenge yourself with a heavier load and maximum intensity to drive home your upper-body gains. Find one exercise trickier than the rest? Give your form one final tweak with the tutorial.


To cool down after training, head to the link at the top of your week of workouts for stretching sessions.
